author: andreasmyth
msg: Use of a ConfigurationBuilder to programmatically obtain and create component configuration.
All configurable components (bus, client and server endpoints, transports etc.) now use the builder to obtain their Configuration.
Added APIs to modify values of configurable properties to Configuration and ConfigurationProvider interfaces.
Implemented a trivial InMemoryProvider that accepts changes (but does not persist them) - enough anyway to programmatically override settings found in defaults, wsdl or Spring config files .
